{"title_page": "Dieter Below", "text_new": "{{short description|German sailor|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2018}}\n{{MedalTableTop}}\n{{MedalSport | [[Sailing (sport)|Sailing]]}}\n{{MedalCountry | {{GDR}} }}\n{{MedalCompetition|[[Olympic Games]]}}\n{{MedalBronze| [[1976 Summer Olympics|1976 Montreal]] | [[Sailing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Soling|Soling class]]}}\n{{MedalBottom}}\n\n'''Dieter Below''' (born 23 June 1942) is a [[Germany|German]] [[sailor]]. He won a bronze medal in the ''[[Soling|Soling Class]]'' with [[Michael Zachries]] and [[Olaf Engelhardt]] at the [[1976 Summer Olympics]] in [[Montreal]].<ref name=\"SR profile\">{{Cite sports-reference | Dieter Below | https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/be/dieter-below-1.html | 29 October 2018 }}</ref>\n{{Footer Dutch Championship Winners in Soling}}\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Below, Dieter}}\n[[Category:1942 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Rostock]]\n[[Category:German male sailors (sport)]]\n[[Category:Olympic sailors of East Germany]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for East Germany]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in sailing]]\n[[Category:Sailors at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Soling]]\n[[Category:Sailors at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Soling]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1976 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:European Champions Soling]]\n\n{{Germany-Olympic-medalist-stub}}\n{{Germany-yachtracing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|German sailor|bot=PearBOT 5}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2018}}\n{{MedalTableTop}}\n{{MedalSport | [[Sailing (sport)|Sailing]]}}\n{{MedalCountry | {{GDR}} }}\n{{MedalCompetition|[[Olympic Games]]}}\n{{MedalBronze| [[1976 Summer Olympics|1976 Montreal]] | [[Sailing at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Soling|Soling class]]}}\n{{MedalBottom}}\n\n'''Dieter Below''' (born 23 June 1942) is a [[Germany|German]] [[sailor]]. He won a bronze medal in the ''[[Soling|Soling Class]]'' with [[Michael Zachries]] and [[Olaf Engelhardt]] at the [[1976 Summer Olympics]] in [[Montreal]].<ref name=\"SR profile\">{{Cite sports-reference | Dieter Below | https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/be/dieter-below-1.html | 29 October 2018 }}</ref>\n{{Footer Dutch Champions in Soling}}\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Below, Dieter}}\n[[Category:1942 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Rostock]]\n[[Category:German male sailors (sport)]]\n[[Category:Olympic sailors of East Germany]]\n[[Category:Olympic bronze medalists for East Germany]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in sailing]]\n[[Category:Sailors at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Soling]]\n[[Category:Sailors at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Soling]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1976 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:European Champions Soling]]\n\n{{Germany-Olympic-medalist-stub}}\n{{Germany-yachtracing-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Dragon Genoa", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dieter_Below"}
